Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides Bowling Alley. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex! I have a question about a charge on my recent bill.

Of course! I’d be happy to help with that. May I have your name, please?

Sure, my name is Jamie.

Thank you, Jamie. To look into your billing details, could you please provide the last four digits of your phone number?

Yes, it’s one two three four.

Great, thank you! And could you also tell me the date you visited us for a better reference?

I visited on October fifth.

Thank you, Jamie. I’ve located your bill and see the charges. Let me clarify any discrepancies.

Thank you for your patience, Jamie. The charge includes your lane rental and shoe rental for two people. Does that match your visit?

Ah, yes, that makes sense now. Thank you for explaining.

You're welcome, Jamie! I'm glad I could help. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
